<plot>A chronicle of a determined little girl's brief journey to satisfy her rather surprising desire. Falling into the category of "edutainment", Cravings, is the first in an ongoing series of CG, animated shorts that combine storytelling with advocacy to present healthy food choices to children (and their families). From a table laden with an assortment of sweets, not far from her slumbering great-grandmother, the child finally manages to grab one of her favorite delicacies.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?117905</url></doc>
